<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="break-out">break out</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>(火灾、战争等) 突然爆发：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Does everyone know what to do if a fire breaks out?
大家都知道发生火灾时该怎么办吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When World War I broke out, he seemed to have become another man, downhearted.
第一次世界大战爆发时，他似乎变成了另一个人，变得非常消沉。</p><footer>2009 湖北</footer></div></div>